title: Google\Cloud\Dlp\V2\ContentLocation
name: ContentLocation
description:

methods.name: getContainerName
methods.description:
Name of the container where the finding is located.

The top level name is the source file name or table name. Nested names could be absent if the embedded object has no string identifier (for an example an image contained within a document).
